knowledge_graph.title: Los Angeles Angels
knowledge_graph.description: The Los Angeles Angels are an American professional baseball team based in the Los Angeles metropolitan area. The Angels compete in Major League Baseball as a member club of the American League West division. Since 1966, the team has played its home games at Angel Stadium in Anaheim, California.
